# Auto Commit, Push, and Deploy After Every Prompt

After making any code changes in response to the user, always run these steps:

1. **Commit and push** to git:
   ```bash
   cd "/Users/samuel/Desktop/CHATGPT CREATED FILES /GIRLS gone digital"
   git add -A && git status
   git commit -m "Brief descriptive message of changes"
   git push
   ```

2. **Deploy to Vercel** so changes go live:
   ```bash
   npx vercel --prod --yes
   ```

The site is live at https://girlsgone.digital. Run these after every prompt that results in file changes.
